{"tid":1325674,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"實況足球獨佔！意甲豪門 Juventus 宣佈與 Konami 達成獨家合作協議","createTime":"2019-07-17T03:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T13:30:45.000Z","uid":1121,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"905ace11db84248c40f13d3f31f06efc1346dae4","tid":1325674,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"《FIFA 20》中將不會出現意甲衛冕冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uaEtbIZNJP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuaEtbIZNJP4&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=26c2da6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uaEtbIZNJP4</a><br />\n<br />\n編輯 : Jas<br />\n意甲豪門 Juventus 日前宣佈與 Konami 達成為期三年的合作協議，雙方將建立長期合作關系，而《Pro Evolution Soccer &ndash; eFootball PES 2020》則成爲唯一擁有「斑馬軍團」官方授權的足球遊戲。據悉《eFootball PES 2020》這款遊戲將獨家使用 Juventus 的知識産權，包括球隊名稱、隊徽和官方隊服，這就意味著《FIFA 20》中將不會出現意甲衛冕冠軍。此外該遊戲的開發團隊將會通過全身 3D 掃描的形式，旨在於遊戲中更加栩栩如生的還原包括 Cristiano Ronaldo 在內的每一位球員。值得一提的是，Juventus 現任副主席、前金球獎得主 Pavel Nedved 也會加入到該遊戲的傳奇球星陣容之中。<br />\n<br />\n據悉新一代《eFootball PES 2020》將在今年 9 月 10 日正式發售，各位遊戲迷不容錯過。"},{"pid":"f46c3b972e8650a2655db29d3b5b106a84e44113","tid":1325674,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"Pes<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60f0e4ba7969f022862d0503fbf853f0af2fe97","tid":1325674,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾祖狗"},{"pid":"db290dd7d09ea157c413c69300d55258069ad195","tid":1325674,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"咁Fifa邊個封面？"},{"pid":"3036b0c62f04236d06486e5f46c388e595d29b5e","tid":1325674,"uid":28574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-